<h1>Introduction</h1>

<p>The Poison Necromancer is a highly gear dependent character that can tackle large groups of mobs at high player numbers on their own. With Poison skills lacking in synergies, it also opens up the ability to mix Poison with other kinds of skills for a big variety. Once geared uip, this is one of the strongest characters in the game for PvE.</p>

<h1>Quick Reference</h1>

<h2>Skill Build</h2>

<p>The following section shows the core skills for the Poison Necromancer. For a detailed breakdown of all core and optional skills as well as the recommended order for allocating skill points, refer to the Skills section of this guide.</p>

<ol>
<li>1 point to all prerequisites</li>
<li>20 points to @@@D2PoisonDagger@@@ - prerequisite for @@@D2PoisonNova@@@, required</li>
<li>20 points to @@@D2PoisonExplosion@@@ - prerequisite for @@@D2PoisonNova@@@, required</li>
<li>20 points to @@@D2PoisonNova@@@ - invest points immediately, required</li>
<li>1-20 points to @@@D2CorpseExplosion@@@ - prerequisite for @@@D2PoisonNova@@@ and good Damage dealer, required</li>
<li>1-X points to @@@D2LowerResist@@@ - Main curse, usually 1 point is enough with Soft Skills but can run more points in it if you want to minmax, required</li>
</ol>

